      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *  CHECK FILEDS OF SCREEN2 (830)
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #CH830    BEGSR
      *
      * CHECK SHIP TO
     C           D2SHPT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,09    D2MSG     P
     C                     SETON                     51  99
     C                     GOTO SKIP2
     C                     ELSE
